        "Status Page: incidents, uptime tracking, maintenance banner, SVG badge",
        "PDF export template (jsPDF) for reports, CVE scans, syslog",
        "User folders, pagination, syslog FTS5 search (#287, gyptazy)",
        "Corporate Layout: light mode polish, icon alignment fixes (#289, #290)",
        "DNS caching — eliminates excessive DNS queries (#279)",
        "fix: cross-cluster replication on ZFS/LVM/iSCSI (#192), bridge format (#274)",
        "fix: rolling update node exclusion (#276), CT keyctl/fuse (#278)",
        "fix: OIDC logout button, SSO re-auth, compliance behind proxy (#281, #294, #295)",
